text: Waratah West is a suburb of Newcastle, New South Wales, Australia, located from Newcastle's central business district. It is part of the City of Newcastle local government area. == History == The Aboriginal people, in this area, the Awabakal, were the first people of this land.School at Waratah West in 1955 ==References== Category:Suburbs of Newcastle, New South Wales
title: Waratah West, New South Wales
